  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether continuous infusion of palonosetron after
      its prophylactic single injection can further reduce the incidence of postoperative nausea
      and vomiting in patients undergoing gynecological laparoscopic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
